                <h1>About FreeCRM</h1>
                <p class="text-justify"><b>What is FreeCRM?</b> FreeCRM is a free Contact Relationship Manager (CRM). 
                  Specifically this CRM is designed for small non-profit organizations that can't 
                  afford other CRMs, but could definitely benefit from the functionality a CRM
                  brings to the table. FreeCRM gives you the ability to enter contact information 
                  for all of your contacts and track contact history, notes, and transactions. 
                  Currently, an email tool is being developed that will allow organizations to send 
                  individual emails to selected contacts on a bulk basis. You will be able to save 
                  email templates and reuse them. Check out the existing functionality below to see
                  if FreeCRM is right for your organization.
                </p>
              </div>
